        <Parent_String>knots (rug components) [300186759], rug components [300205011], coverings and hangings components [300186754], furnishings components [300241953], components by specific context [300241584], components (objects parts) [300241583], Components (hierarchy name) [300241490], Objects Facet [300264092]</Parent_String>
